person.persName: Elkanah Winne (Owsley County, KY, innkeeper and Owsley County Court Clerk)

body.p: Owsley County, Kentucky, innkeeper and court clerk. Virginia native. Married to Eudocia Winne. Innkeeper in Booneville, Kentucky, in 1860. Father of William Winne. Clerk in Owsley County Court in Owsley County from 1862 to 1866.
